pullRequest.body:
Defines `FirstOrder.Language.BoundedFormula.IsDNF` and `FirstOrder.Language.BoundedFormula.IsCNF` for conjunctive and disjunctive normal forms. Defines `FirstOrder.Language.BoundedFormula.toDNF` and `FirstOrder.Language.BoundedFormula.toCNF` for converting bounded formulas to conjunctive and disjunctive normal forms.

---
